   unique opportunity to disrupt established norms through their
   representations of esports competitors. This study analyzes the
   representation of U.S. Army Esports (USAE) team members via official
   social media channels. USAE was created as a public relations tool to
   engage with a younger audience, redefine the public image of the Army,
