   lexical items. The results show that there exists a stable vocabulary
   core of 2,122 items (70.7\%) among the four corpora. Moreover, these
   vocabulary items occur with comparable ranks in the individual
   wordlists. In producing the new-GSL, the core vocabulary items were
   combined with new items frequently occurring in the corpora representing
