Abstract = {What is the relationship between interpretive methods and decolonizing
   projects? Decolonial thinkers often invoke pre-colonial traditions in
   their efforts to fashion ``national cultures{''}- modes of being,
   understanding, and self-expression specific to a de-colonizing
   collectivity's experience. While the substantive contributions of
